This Tutorial is for Rest Api

Express is a fast,light and free web framework for nodejs
Express makes building web application with Nodejs much easier
Express has full control over request and response

nodejs/express middleware
    - acts as a bridge in any request
    - have access to request and response where you can manipulate the request and response before it goes in and out of the endpoint/routes

note
    array.map
    array.filter <- can return a value
    array.forEach